The following tests are conducted (see Schneider Electric - Site Acceptance test protocol for results and trends):
•	Load Transfer test
•	Inverter to bypass transition on NO LOAD
•	Inverter to bypass transition on FULL LOAD
•	Load step test (0%-50%-0%)
•	Load step test (25%-75%-25%)
•	Load step test (50%-100%-50%)
•	Load step test (75%-100%-75%)
•	Load step test (0%-100%-0%)
•	THDi and THDv measurements (0%, 25%, 50%,75%, 100%)
•	Expected Results: Total Harmonic Distortion (THD) is to be under 5%
•	UPS efficiency calculation (Unity PF@0%, 25%, 50%, 75%, 100%)
•	UPS battery discharge test (15min EOL)
